page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content: This survey was performed by children in class 5 of Copplestone School, the third and fourth year Juniors: Richard Appleyard, Natalie Barber, Natalie Bore, Stewart Bragg, Rebecca Clason, Christopher Drew, Kelly Hemsley, Rachel Horton, David Hunt, Steven Jarvis, Sharon Jewell, Richard John, Paul Kingdon, Tracy Lay, Branwell Moffat, Kate Moorhouse, Mark Oliver, Mathew Penny, Joanna Petherick, Lucy Pluck, Kathy Pugsley, Jason Rice, Caroline Rookes, Nicholas Southwood, Melanie Stanbury, Tom Stephenson, Simon Tucker, Jane Walton, and Ruth Warren, with a little help from Mr Brown. The slides are the work of Jeremy Bore of Tondal Photographic Services.
